title: 12/11: Waiver Wire (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
Are Fantasy owners ready to turn to Elijah McGuire and Marcus Murphy? Will Dante Pettis come through again? Which DSTs will lead you to the Finals? We start with our top priorities before giving a sneak peak at each position (6:53) and looking ahead to Week 16 (18:35) ... Recapping MIN-SEA (20:50) and LAR-CHI (25:52). What a couple of duds! Did anything encouraging come from these games or do we have rest of season concerns about these QBs? ... Waiver Wire QBs (29:50) including Lamar Jackson and Josh Allen, RBs (38:30) including Doug Martin, Derrick Henry and Kenneth Dixon, WRs (46:50) including Curtis Samuel and Isaiah McKenzie, TEs (52:55) including Ian Thomas and Anthony Firkser, plus DSTs at the end of the show ... Email us at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
